Package: cryptocoins
Type: Package
Title: Methods and data for dealing with Cryptocurrencies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Guilherme Duarte
Maintainer: Guilherme Duarte <gjardimduarte at gmail.com>
Description: This packages helps users deal with data from cryptocoins, such as
  Bitcoin (BTC) or Ethereum (ETH). It provides exchange rate data and methods 
  for technical analysis. It relies on packages 'tidyquant' and POLONIEX API. 
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  tidyverse,
  forcats,
  tidyquant,
  jsonlite
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
